<TITLE>First Stage of Radio nuclides Release.</TITLE>
<H3><IMG SRC  = "polyn0.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE><I>Russian Research Center "Kurchatov Institute"</I></H3>
<H2>Hypertext Data base:<B> Chernobyl and its consequences</B>.(<I>Project "Polyn"</I>).</H2>
<HR>
<H1>First Stage of Radionuclides Release.</H1>
<HR>
     At the first stage the mechanical release  of  the  dispersed 
fuel took  place  as  a  result  of  the  initial  explosion.  Its 
radionuclide composition corresponds to fuel inventory of the core 
with enrichment by volatile nuclides  of  iodine,  tellurium,  and 
cesium (Load <A HREF = "rstages.gif">picture</A> for illustration if it is needed). 
<HR> 
See also: <A HREF = "coreinv.html">Core Inventory</A>, <A HREF = "rbmkshrt.html">RBMK reactor</A>, <A HREF = "contents.html">Contents</A>. 
<HR> 
