<LI><A HREF="news:alt.smokers.pipes">Alt.Smokers.Pipes</A> - Pipes discussion group (if your browser agrees).<p>
<LI><a href="http://www.pipes.org/subscribe.html">subscribe</a> to The Pipes Digest Mailing List.
</UL>
